`}</code></pre>
    <p>{`Do not forget that this feature is available only for IIS 7.5 and above. Also, do not forget that you may have to do some additional code if you want to use your repository with your IoC container. If you are using the Http Cache that Asp.Net provides, you need to have the namespace added to your project that has the custom provider.`}</p>

